oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Country Music Awards interviews - Biff Collie - 1966
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Recording of various artist and music industry representative interviews, conducted by Biff Collie and the 1966 Country Music Award show.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Biff Collie introduces Rex Allen -- Rex Allen talks about performing at the awards show and all the other talent -- Biff Collie introduces Freddie Hart -- Freddie Hart talks about performing at the awards show and thanks Biff -- Collie introduces Pewdie Smith -- Smith talks about enjoying the awards show -- Collie introduces Chill Wills -- Wills talks about the awards show -- Collie introduces Jimmy Bourne -- Bourne thanks Biff and praises Dean Martin -- Collie introduces Dick Link -- Link talks about presenting at the award show and all the celebrities he manages -- Collie introduces Tom Palomino -- Tom Palomino thanks Biff -- Collie introduces the Lauren Green -- Lauren Green talks about the award show and thanks Biff -- Collie introduces Donna [Unidentified] -- Donna thanks Biff -- Collie introduces Slim Pickens -- Pickens thanks Biff and talks about what he said on stage -- Collie introduces Molly B -- Molly talks about performing at the awards show and what she is wearing -- Collie introduces Jed Clamped -- Jed talks about the award show -- Collie introduces Donna Lauren -- Donna Lauren talks -- Bob Morris talks about winning an award -- Collie introduces Granny and Gomer of the Beverly Hillbillies -- Collie introduces Dick Clark -- Clark talks about the awards show -- Clark talks about country music being the biggest influence in music -- Collie introduces Anita Kerr -- Kerr talks about her influence -- Dick Scofield talks about Biff Collie being a great disc jockey -- Buck Owens talks about Biff Collie -- Biff Collie talks about the award he won -- Buck Owens thanks Biff -- Tennessee Ernie Ford talks about the awards show -- [Unidentified] talks -- Kay Adams talks and thanks Biff -- Judy Lynn talks and congratulates Biff on his award -- Jim Brown congratulates Biff and talks about the award show
